Version 0.3
-----------

 * Now it initializes the resource if params[:id] is nil
 * Hence name changed to find_or_initialize_resource
 * :also_filter option, adds actions to the filter list

Version 0.2
-----------

 * create_resource_finder must be called for the finder to be created
 * :model option to create_resource_finder specifies the model to be found
 * :context option to create_resource_finder specifies the context to find in (ie. current_user.posts)
 * All other options are passed to find

Version 0.1
-----------

 * Initial release
